title: How to keep going on your diet after the new year's excitement wears off
description:
Get the Free Course here:
https://phit.click/freecourse

 

It's so easy to be excited for weightloss on January 1. But what do you do a week later when the newness wears off? How do you show up each day when you just want to eat a little? Today I teach you the #1 thing you must know so you don't give up on your weightloss goals.
